original_title: UFC Fight Night 10: Stout vs. Fisher
overview: UFC Fight Night 10: Stout vs. Fisher was a mixed martial arts event held by the Ultimate Fighting Championship on Tuesday, June 12, 2007, at the Seminole Hard Rock Hotel and Casino in Hollywood, Florida. The main event was a rematch from a UFC 58 fight in which Fisher was a late replacement for Stouts opponent, and he had to cut a lot of water weight just to fight. Stout won their first fight by split decision.
title: UFC Fight Night 10: Stout vs. Fisher
